metadata.name: GENESIS / MEKANIK DOLL
metadata.description:
GENESIS / MEKANIK DOLL

~ The future owner of this one will probably have the most important piece of my art career, the start of something new, of something I dream for a long time,  be able to create something new, a unique aesthetic, something rare,  something that will define my art forever. ~ 


Created in July 2022 / Sculpted and rendered in 3D
